<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <section id="reviews-355">
      <div class="cs-container">
        <div class="cs-content">
          <span class="cs-topper lora-reviews-text">Happy Clients</span>
          <h2 class="cs-title lora-reviews-text">Our Reviews</h2>
          <p class="cs-text lora-reviews-text">
            Hear from those who have trusted us to make their events truly
            special.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-carousel">
          <ul class="cs-card-group">
            <li class="cs-item">
              <img
                class="cs-quote"
                aria-hidden="true"
                src="/public/svg/stars.svg"
                decoding="async"
                alt="star icon"
                width="40"
                height="33"
              />
              <p class="cs-review lora-reviews-text">
                "The team was fantastic. They were friendly, easy to work with,
                and understood exactly what I wanted. The quality of their work
                was excellent, and they delivered everything on time and within
                budget. I'm really impressed and would definitely recommend
                them."
              </p>
              <span class="cs-name lora-reviews-text">Sahana.R</span>
              <span class="cs-job lora-reviews-text"></span>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
              <img
                class="cs-quote"
                aria-hidden="true"
                src="/public/svg/stars.svg"
                decoding="async"
                alt="quote icon"
                width="40"
                height="33"
              />
              <p class="cs-review lora-reviews-text">
                "Shubh Sandharbh nailed it! They planned my son's wedding and
                reception flawlessly. Every detail was covered, and our guests
                loved it."
              </p>
              <span class="cs-name lora-reviews-text"
                >Chandra Shekaran Natarajan</span
              >
              <span class="cs-job lora-reviews-text"></span>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
              <img
                class="cs-quote"
                aria-hidden="true"
                src="/public/svg/stars.svg"
                decoding="async"
                alt="quote icon"
                width="40"
                height="33"
              />
              <p class="cs-review lora-reviews-text">
                "Thank you Ganavi and Team. Absolutely loved the decoration. One
                of the best event team I have come across."
              </p>
              <span class="cs-name lora-reviews-text">Priyanka</span>
              <span class="cs-job lora-reviews-text"></span>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
              <img
                class="cs-quote"
                aria-hidden="true"
                src="/public/svg/stars.svg"
                decoding="async"
                alt="quote icon"
                width="40"
                height="33"
              />
              <p class="cs-review lora-reviews-text">
                It was a dream come true for our wedding planning! Their
                patience and expertise made the entire process stress free.
                Ganavi and Uttam were absolutely wonderful to work with them
                they truly made our day unforgettable.
              </p>
              <span class="cs-name lora-reviews-text">Vikas Gupta</span>
              <span class="cs-job lora-reviews-text"></span>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
              <img
                class="cs-quote"
                aria-hidden="true"
                src="/public/svg/stars.svg"
                decoding="async"
                alt="quote icon"
                width="40"
                height="33"
              />
              <p class="cs-review lora-reviews-text">
                "Indianest Events was incredible! Their constant support and
                guidance throughout the planning process made our wedding day a
                dream come true. We couldn't have asked for a better team."
              </p>
              <span class="cs-name lora-reviews-text"
                ><strong>Gunjan.T</strong></span
              >
              <span class="cs-job lora-reviews-text"></span>
            </li>
            <li class="cs-item">
              <img
                class="cs-quote"
                aria-hidden="true"
                src="/public/svg/stars.svg"
                decoding="async"
                alt="quote icon"
                width="40"
                height="33"
              />
              <p class="cs-review lora-reviews-text">
                "Their team handled everything with care, from the beautiful
                decor to the seamless coordination of events. They went above
                and beyond to bring our vision to life, stress-free celebration.
                I highly recommend them for any special occasion!"
              </p>
              <span class="cs-name lora-reviews-text"
                ><strong></strong>Kiran Kumar</span
              >
              <span class="cs-job lora-reviews-text"></span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <style>
      .lora-reviews-text {
        font-family: "Lora", serif;
        font-optical-sizing: auto;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-style: normal;
      }

      :root {
        --primary: #ff6a3e;
        --primaryLight: #ffba43;
        --secondary: #ffba43;
        --secondaryLight: #ffba43;
        --headerColor: #1a1a1a;
        --bodyTextColor: #4e4b66;
        --bodyTextColorWhite: #fafbfc;
        --topperFontSize: clamp(0.8125rem, 1.6vw, 1rem);
        --headerFontSize: clamp(1.9375rem, 3.9vw, 3.0625rem);
        --bodyFontSize: 1rem;
        --sectionPadding: clamp(3.75rem, 7.82vw, 6.25rem) 1rem;
        --backgroundColor: #e2d9b9;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      *,
      *:before,
      *:after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .cs-topper {
        font-size: var(--topperFontSize);
        line-height: 1.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-align: inherit;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        display: block;
      }

      .cs-title {
        font-size: var(--headerFontSize);
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1.2em;
        text-align: inherit;
        max-width: 43.75rem;
        margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        color: var(--headerColor);
        position: relative;
      }

      .cs-text {
        font-size: var(--bodyFontSize);
        line-height: 1.5em;
        text-align: inherit;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 40.625rem;
        margin: 0;
        color: black;
      }

      #reviews-355 {
        padding: clamp(3.75rem, 7.82vw, 6.25rem) 1rem;
        background-color: var(--backgroundColor);
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 90rem;
        margin: auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-content {
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-carousel {
        width: 100%;
        overflow-x: auto;
        scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-card-group {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        scroll-snap-align: start;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        gap: 1rem;
        overflow: auto;
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-item {
        list-style: none;
        width: 100%;
        padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3.15vw, 2rem) clamp(1rem, 3.15vw, 2.5rem);
        background-color: #fff8ec;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
        scroll-snap-align: center;
        position: relative;
        border-style: solid;
        border-color: #fbf0e3;
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-quote {
        width: clamp(10.5625rem, 20vw, 11.8125rem);
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        display: block;
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-review {
        font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
        line-height: 1.5em;
        font-weight: 400;
        text-align: left;
        color: var(--bodyTextColor);
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-name {
        font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
        line-height: 1.5em;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: left;
        color: var(--headerColor);
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      #reviews-355 .cs-job {
        font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);
        line-height: 1.5em;
        font-weight: 400;
        text-align: left;
        color: var(--primary);
        display: block;
      }

      @media only screen and (min-width: 48rem) {
        #reviews-355 .cs-item {
          width: clamp(25.5%, 30vw, 32.3%);
        }
      }

      /* Additional styles for improved desktop view */
      @media only screen and (min-width: 48rem) {
        #reviews-355 .cs-carousel {
          flex-direction: row;
          overflow-x: hidden;
          padding: 0;
        }

        #reviews-355 .cs-card-group {
          display: flex;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          gap: 2rem;
          padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        #reviews-355 .cs-item {
          width: 30%;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          border: none;
          transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        #reviews-355 .cs-item:hover {
          box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        #reviews-355 .cs-review {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }

        #reviews-355 .cs-name {
          font-size: 1.125rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
